00:12:21.610 --> 00:12:22.850
types are in different apps?

00:12:22.990 --> 00:12:23.720
That's awesome, you know.

00:12:23.750 --> 00:12:25.860
It's a very cool selling point for app proto.

00:12:26.670 --> 00:12:30.360
And developers can publish their own types and contribute to what's

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:32.380
already, like, a very rich ecosystem.

